jsku karticu (brevet) i diplomu za ronjenje do 20 m dubine\r\n- 12 sati teorijskih predavanja\r\n- 6 sati vježbi u bazenu\r\n- zarone u moru\r\n- udžbenik\r\n- dnevnik zarona\r\n- DVD s vježbama\r\n- etui i plastične dekompresijske tablice\r\n- naljepnice RK Geronimo i Hrvatskog ronilačkog saveza\r\nCijena tečaja ne uključuje troškove putovanja i smještaja na moru (cca 500,- kn).\r\nZanimaju li te dodatne informacije, javi nam se putem maila: <a href=\"mailto:ronilacki.tecajevi@rkgeronimo.hr\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">ronilacki.tecajevi@rkgeronimo.hr</a>','Početni ronilački tečaj','','publish','closed','closed','','pocetni-ronilacki-tecaj-4','','','2022-10-23 11:43:22','2022-10-23 10:43:22','',0,'http://local.rkgeronimo/?post_type=course&#038;p=96',0,'course','',0),(105,2207,'2022-10-11 04:20:16','2022-10-11 03:20:16','','Ulaz u Lucice','','inherit','closed','closed','','ulaz-u-lucice','','','2022-10-11 04:20:16','2022-10-11 03:20:16','',103,'http://local.rkgeronimo/app/uploads/2022/10/Ulaz-u-Lucice.jpeg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(109,2207,'2022-10-11 04:26:10','2022-10-11 03:26:10','','DC','','inherit','closed','closed','','dc','','','2022-10-11 04:26:10','2022-10-11 03:26:10','',107,'http://local.rkgeronimo/app/uploads/2022/10/DC.jpeg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(110,2207,'2022-10-11 04:26:10','2022-10-11 03:26:10','','gumenjak','','inherit','closed','closed','','gumenjak','','','2022-10-11 04:26:10','2022-10-11 03:26:10','',107,'http://local.rkgeronimo/app/uploads/2022/10/gumenjak.jpeg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(115,2207,'2022-10-13 14:46:13','2022-10-13 13:46:13','{\"version\": 2, \"isGlobalStylesUserThemeJSON\": true }','Custom Styles','','publish','closed','closed','','wp-global-styles-rkg-theme','','','2022-10-13 14:46:13','2022-10-13 13:46:13','',0,'http://local.rkgeronimo/?p=115',0,'wp_global_styles','',0),(175,2207,'2022-11-05 16:18:36','2022-11-05 15:18:36','','RK Geronimo','','inherit','closed','closed','','android-ch